## ğŸ’» Developer Setup (Optional)
If you want to run or modify the TypeScript frontend locally:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Finance-Insight-Lab/bt-visualizer.git
cd bt-visualizer

npm install
npm run dev
```
This will start the development server.


